Class WkfTracking

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.axelor.db.Model
      • com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
        • com.axelor.studio.db.WkfTracking

  • @Entity
public class WkfTracking
extends com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
    This object store workflow realted tracking information for an object. It will store information like number of time some status changed, or changed by which user with date and time. Entry will be created on onSave of related object.
